# RPG UI Theming

## Objective
Apply a comprehensive global theme matching the desired Gamified DevHouse aesthetic.

## Tasks
1. Refine the Tailwind configuration with chosen typography, deep background colors, and active accent colors.
2. Ensure buttons, input fields, and modals look cohesive and stylized consistently.
3. Polish hover states, focusing on a tactile, responsive feel.
